Package: rforceplots
Type: Package
Title: Additive Force Plots based on SHAP and shapjs
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Rafael", "Henkin",
                    email = "r.henkin@qmul.ac.uk", 
                    role = c("aut", "cre")),
            person("Scott", "Lundberg", role = c("ctb","cph"), comment = "shapjs javascript package" )
            )
Maintainer: Rafael Henkin <r.henkin@qmul.ac.uk>
Description: The package is a stand-alone wrapper for the shapjs package to facilitate rendering additive force plots in R.
  It has a user-friendly function for plotting, Shiny bindings, compatibility with the shapr and shapper packages, and bindings for the three base visualisation functions from shapjs.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/rhenkin/rforceplots
BugReports: https://github.com/rhenkin/rforceplots/issues
